{"about_the_game":"<strong>One True Hero</strong> is a quirky <strong>3D platforming adventure</strong> featuring a young hero who can barely save himself!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>An Epic Adventure</strong></h2>\u200bAn evil tyrant... A magic sword... A young farmer turned <strong>Hero</strong>...<br>It's a tale we've heard thousands of times before, and in the kingdom of Genericia things like that happen every other week! <br>This makes it hard for our Hero to be taken seriously when he tries to save a town that's mysteriously sinking into the ground, even if he is the only one capable of saving it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/Adventure.gif?t=1706800488\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Nerve-Racking Sword Fights</strong></h2>All sorts of terrible evil creatures will stand in your path. You're going to have to deal with them if you want to save the kingdom!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/Combat.gif?t=1706800488\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Loads of Platforming</strong></h2>Who knew there was so much jumping involved in being a legendary hero?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/Platforming.gif?t=1706800488\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Tale to Remember</strong></h2>Meet a cast of memorable characters, explore dungeons, solve puzzles and unravel the mystery of the sinking town before it disappears off the face of the earth!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/Tale.gif?t=1706800488\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Will you be the One True Hero this kingdom needs?</strong></h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ding Dong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1596170/397ae07fe5b08